data.description: Lake Texoma, BEAUTIFUL 3.34 ac property! Rare find on Preston Peninsula. This large lot has been cleared and fenced, with two ponds and a circular drive in the front of property. Home is 2356 sq ft and comes with lots of upgrades! Textured walls, cedar beams, wood laminate floors throughout, upgraded LARGE shower in master. Game room can be used as a second master with an attached bathroom and dual sinks. Kitchen has brand new microwave and all electric appliances, new septic pump in December 2021. Built in desk and cabinets in hallway, large laundry room. Fenced dog area in back. Strapped, concrete beam foundation. 3 outside water bibs.
